Darkness Radio enters Portals to Hell with special guests Jack Osbourne & Katrina Weidman!

Jack Osbourne and Katrina Weidman resume their chilling journey to historically haunted locations in the United States, confronting sinister stories of the supernatural as they seek concrete evidence that a spirit world exists.

All this PLUS Supernatural News and YOUR paranormal encounters on this weeks edition of Darkness Radio.

Descend into all-new eerie encounters when Travel Channel’s hit series, "Portals to Hell," returns for Season Two on Thursday April 30th.
